; Regression test for issue #1675: assertion fails when account is emptied
; via balance assignment and a sub-account receives the balancing amount.
; account("parent").total was returning double the correct value (230
; instead of 115) because family_details were not properly reset after
; the balance assignment added a new posting.

2018-08-25
    source
    parent               100
    parent:child1         10
    parent:child2          5

assert account("parent").total == 115

2018-08-25
    parent               = 0
    parent:child3

assert account("parent").total == 115

test bal
                 115  parent
                  10    child1
                   5    child2
                 100    child3
                -115  source
--------------------
                   0
end test
